data.description: Welcome to Amberley Forest! You'll love this low-maintenance home conveniently located in the heart of Virginia Beach and surrounding military bases! Open kitchen with custom cabinetry, granite countertops complete with a stainless- steel range & microwave. New carpet in master bedroom, stairs and entire upstairs. Roof and heating & air all less than 8 years old. With 2 bedrooms up and 2 bedrooms down, there is great potential to use one as a "flex" game room or office. There's just enough room on the back deck and in the fenced -in yard to have a cozy entertaining space without a lot of up- keep.
